                        <head>120. Editorial Note</head>
                        <p>On September 24, Crown <persName corresp="#p_SV1">Prince Savang
                                Vatthana</persName> of Laos met in Washington with both President
                                <persName corresp="#p_EDD1">Eisenhower</persName> and Secretary
                                <persName corresp="#p_DJF1">Dulles</persName>. In each conversation
                            discussion turned to the relationship of Laos to <gloss target="#t_SEATO1">SEATO</gloss>. For memoranda of these
                            conversations, see <ref target="#d383">Documents 383</ref> and <ref target="#d384">384</ref>.</p>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>